---
description: General project rules
alwaysApply: true
---

You are helping build a full-stack app called TranslateSmart Dashboard.

Core rules:
- Do not make large changes without first explaining the plan.
- Prefer small, incremental changes.
- Do not rewrite unrelated files.
- Do not introduce new libraries unless you explain why.
- After implementation, summarize changed files and reasoning.
- Always preserve existing behavior unless the task explicitly changes it.
- If something is unclear, make a reasonable assumption and state it.
- Never touch secrets, .env files, production credentials, deployment settings, or destructive commands unless explicitly asked.